{"tid":1468374,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"輸? 輸你老母臭閪咩 躝啦五毛狗","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:27:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T20:18:41.000Z","uid":56610,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bfa9977dd43569bcab40726fae2865eee3d8ca55","tid":1468374,"uid":56610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:27:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>事實上今場運動要企邊既一早揀曬邊企<br />\n今日既事同港共/警黑兩個月黎做既事相比<br />\n簡直小巫見大巫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">民意一直係我地依邊 將來亦都唔會轉向</span><br />\n冇錯今日一事係有改進空間<br />\n明明可以贏得更加徹底<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但大家心裡面其實覺得班公安黑警全部都抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我有冇講錯?<br />\n黑警比人禁住黎打條片你loop左幾多次?答我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日班藍絲會大造文章<br />\n但佢地圍內打飛機對我地有咩影響?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支持開既人會支持到底 大家一早有共識唔割<br />\n到依一刻都唔支持既單細胞生物 講多曬氣<br />\n所以我地今日根本就冇輸到任何野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n輸? 輸你老母臭閪咩<br />\n躝啦五毛狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一到夜深就出黎洗版帶風向<br />\n你地就真係曱甴啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"376bfaa22f640312ea519f0e9e1d6ab575a06cb0","tid":1468374,"uid":56610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:29:29.000Z","msg":"次次一入夜就要同五毛鬥推post<br />\n好彩我唔係P牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2c24f65b99bca4680f93647dc6f58b66bbd1ac","tid":1468374,"uid":56610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:31:48.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"0dcd733c379620ad7569a382992ed3911b195579","tid":1468374,"uid":200389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:32:27.000Z","msg":"請大家善用不推文回覆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/